title: Condoleeza Rice, Weather Report, Alec Baldwin, Wrong Damn Wedding and more.

description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! Can a simple phone call lead to the end of one's life? Rev. Adnoid threw Deacon Def Jam under the bus. Somebody got a nosy spirit that makes no damn sense to The CLO. Certain things only happen to and with J. Anthony Brown. We pray for those involved in the incident on the Alec Baldwin movie set. "Condi" had some things to say about critical race theory. Mother Nature is undefeated. Have certain things happened to you if dairy has ever touched your digestive tract? Comedy Roulette will remind you of thundercats lookin' 30! Today the show wraps up with Blue Cheese talking about his trending style.
